333
00:15:07,540 --> 00:15:09,370
If I keep taking these tonics,

334
00:15:10,120 --> 00:15:11,920
I'll either die from overeating

335
00:15:12,330 --> 00:15:14,280
or from blood loss.

336
00:15:15,110 --> 00:15:18,170
