341
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:35,320
Shoukang Palace?

342
00:15:35,670 --> 00:15:37,200
This person came just in time.

343
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:39,530
How about trying my luck with Du Sanniang?

344
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:46,090
Actually,

345
00:15:46,830 --> 00:15:48,800
I have an unreasonable request,

346
00:15:48,840 --> 00:15:51,100
