350
00:15:57,150 --> 00:15:57,680
Hurry up!

351
00:15:58,150 --> 00:15:59,000
Pour the wine.

352
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:00,260
Let me refill your cup.

353
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:04,630
