to pay respects to him.

451
00:20:39,160 --> 00:20:40,400
I'm so sad about that.

452
00:20:41,290 --> 00:20:42,170
Therefore,

453
00:20:42,480 --> 00:20:43,280
I have decided

454
00:20:43,370 --> 00:20:46,670
