459
00:20:56,560 --> 00:20:58,240
You two, be careful.

460
00:20:58,370 --> 00:20:59,530
Hang them neatly.

461
00:21:00,270 --> 00:21:01,590
Don't just stand there. Go over there.

462
00:21:01,590 --> 00:21:02,320
Hang them up.

463
00:21:03,190 --> 00:21:03,950
Be careful.

464
00:21:03,970 --> 00:21:04,730
Slow down.

465
00:21:04,750 --> 00:21:06,550
These things are very valuable.

466
00:21:13,560 --> 00:21:15,320
Dear, are you not satisfied?

467
00:21:16,680 --> 00:21:17,700
It's alright.

468
00:21:18,260 --> 00:21:20,070
I've also hired a shaman.

469
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:21,240
A shaman?

470
00:21:21,560 --> 00:21:22,630
Yes, a shaman.

471
00:21:23,540 --> 00:21:26,120
