00:27:38,850 --> 00:27:40,450
for the vast world

564
00:27:41,370 --> 00:27:43,970
and for the peace and
prosperity of all people,

565
00:27:44,070 --> 00:27:46,680
I should bear the burden in court

566
00:27:47,790 --> 00:27:50,590
and face numerous difficulties
without regrets.

567
00:27:50,910 --> 00:27:52,110
Is it worth it?

568
00:27:54,540 --> 00:27:55,300
Yes.

569
00:28:05,130 --> 00:28:06,060
What's wrong?

570
00:28:06,090 --> 00:28:07,090
Are you troubled?

571
00:28:07,830 --> 00:28:08,580
Yes.

572
00:28:10,810 --> 00:28:11,900
I'm troubled.

573
00:28:13,610 --> 00:28:15,050
The way you are now

574
00:28:15,410 --> 00:28:16,950
is nothing like when you used to shout that

575
00:28:16,950 --> 00:28:18,150
you are my husband

576
00:28:18,180 --> 00:28:19,500
and tell me to obey you.

577
00:28:22,120 --> 00:28:24,860
At that time, the palace guards were
all surrounding us outside.

578
00:28:24,860 --> 00:28:26,460
You were in imminent danger.

579
00:28:26,500 --> 00:28:28,050
I was anxious.

580
00:28:28,340 --> 00:28:29,220
About what?

581
00:28:29,480 --> 00:28:31,280
You were afraid I'd be captured?

582
00:28:32,180 --> 00:28:33,020
Yes.

583
00:28:34,830 --> 00:28:36,830
I was afraid they would capture you.

584
00:28:38,160 --> 00:28:39,960
I was afraid they would hurt you.

585
00:28:42,220 --> 00:28:44,820
I was even more afraid that
they would kill you.

586
00:28:45,590 --> 00:28:47,980
What if they had really captured me?

587
00:28:48,010 --> 00:28:50,210
I would do whatever it takes to save you.

588
00:28:52,670 --> 00:28:53,220
Yunqing.

589
00:28:54,370 --> 00:28:55,450
To me,

590
00:28:57,490 --> 00:29:00,150
your life is more important
than anything else.

591
00:29:01,740 --> 00:29:02,540
In the future,

592
00:29:02,770 --> 00:29:04,880
perhaps we can live an ordinary life.

593
00:29:04,930 --> 00:29:06,190
We can leave the capital

594
00:29:06,190 --> 00:29:08,220
and these places of conflicts.

595
00:29:12,730 --> 00:29:13,970
You're wavering.

596
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:15,420
I'm not.

597
00:29:16,170 --> 00:29:18,300
You still want to assist Huo Jingheng?

598
00:29:18,330 --> 00:29:20,350
Have you forgotten that he shot
an arrow at you two years ago?

599
00:29:20,350 --> 00:29:21,510
No, I haven't.

600
00:29:23,270 --> 00:29:25,580
Back then, you stood in the way
of his ascension to the throne.

601
00:29:25,580 --> 00:29:27,200
That was why he wanted to kill you.

602
00:29:27,200 --> 00:29:28,600
Now he's trying to use you

603
00:29:28,600 --> 00:29:30,030
to consolidate his imperial power.

604
00:29:30,030 --> 00:29:31,940
If the same situation arises again,

605
00:29:31,940 --> 00:29:32,870
he'll still do the same thing.

606
00:29:32,870 --> 00:29:33,980
Alright, Yunqing.

607
00:29:42,610 --> 00:29:43,460
I'm sorry.

608
00:29:44,150 --> 00:29:45,550
Early tomorrow morning,

609
00:29:46,370 --> 00:29:47,830
I will take you all away.

610
00:29:59,850 --> 00:30:00,610
Yue Chi.

611
00:30:01,200 --> 00:30:02,400
Don't let me down.

612
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:04,200
Leave Huo Jingheng.

613
00:30:25,070 --> 00:30:25,610
Brother.

614
00:30:27,310 --> 00:30:29,310
Do you already know everything?

615
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,390
If I had not known it,

616
00:30:32,980 --> 00:30:34,980
would you keep it from me forever?

617
00:30:36,010 --> 00:30:37,590
That's not what I meant.

618
00:30:38,990 --> 00:30:42,190
You and Huo Jingheng conspired
to lure me into the palace.

619
00:30:42,620 --> 00:30:44,880
Then you led me into
his trap step by step.

620
00:30:47,240 --> 00:30:49,370
What situation do you want to put me in?

621
00:30:49,830 --> 00:30:50,440
I...

622
00:30:55,240 --> 00:30:56,070
Brother.

623
00:30:56,830 --> 00:30:58,030
Don't be angry.

624
00:31:05,030 --> 00:31:05,790
Brother.

625
00:31:06,370 --> 00:31:09,250
Do you really not want to return to court?

626
00:31:10,200 --> 00:31:12,740
When you established the
Rongying Academy with Huo Jingheng,

627
00:31:12,740 --> 00:31:14,540
you were happy too, weren't you?

628
00:31:15,780 --> 00:31:17,020
During that time,

629
00:31:17,100 --> 00:31:19,810
there was always a smile on your face.

630
00:31:22,360 --> 00:31:24,290
But I haven't seen a smile

631
00:31:24,590 --> 00:31:26,450
like that on your face for so long.

632
00:31:26,680 --> 00:31:28,320
That was the real you.

633
00:31:29,160 --> 00:31:30,620
You cared about the world.

634
00:31:30,900 --> 00:31:32,920
You were high-spirited and vigorous.

635
00:31:32,920 --> 00:31:34,270
You've never changed.

636
00:31:34,270 --> 00:31:36,030
What he wants is not only me

637
00:31:36,400 --> 00:31:38,350
but also the Qilin Army behind me.

638
00:31:39,200 --> 00:31:41,260
The imperial power is a fierce beast.

639
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:42,950
The Emperor's thoughts are unpredictable.

640
00:31:42,950 --> 00:31:45,050
He might kill people
and destroy their spirits.

641
00:31:45,050 --> 00:31:47,450
I can't take a risk with
all our lives again.

642
00:31:48,630 --> 00:31:49,630
Actually,

643
00:31:51,680 --> 00:31:53,500
Huo Jingheng might be a good Emperor.

644
00:31:53,500 --> 00:31:54,890
If you like him so much,

645
00:31:56,060 --> 00:31:57,060
you can stay.

646
00:31:58,580 --> 00:31:59,560
I'll leave.

647
00:32:00,590 --> 00:32:01,120
Brother.

648
00:32:03,030 --> 00:32:04,720
Actually, I came here today

649
00:32:05,460 --> 00:32:07,250
to return this to you.

650
00:32:16,290 --> 00:32:18,360
[Records of Dog Huo's Daily Life]

651
00:32:24,030 --> 00:32:26,530
[Records of Dog Huo's Daily Life]

652
00:32:34,060 --> 00:32:36,260
If your brother were still alive today,

653
00:32:36,810 --> 00:32:39,270
he would surely have
achieved great things.

654
00:32:39,610 --> 00:32:41,380
For the vast world

655
00:32:42,670 --> 00:32:45,290
and for the peace and
prosperity of all people...

656
00:32:45,290 --> 00:32:48,630
I should bear the burden in court.

657
