Have you forgotten that he shot
an arrow at you two years ago?

658
00:33:03,780 --> 00:33:06,280
Back then, you stood in the way
of his ascension to the throne.

659
00:33:06,280 --> 00:33:08,140
That was why he wanted to kill you.

660
00:33:59,360 --> 00:34:00,200
In the future,

661
00:34:00,390 --> 00:34:02,480
perhaps we can live an ordinary life.

662
00:34:02,520 --> 00:34:04,720
We can leave these places of conflicts.

663
00:34:30,050 --> 00:34:30,810
Don't worry.

664
00:34:32,469 --> 00:34:35,469
I've allowed you to live
a peaceful life for two years.

665
00:34:35,659 --> 00:34:38,389
Because I didn't want to
force you to do anything.

666
00:34:39,560 --> 00:34:41,020
I just want to tell you that

667
00:34:41,530 --> 00:34:42,969
as long as you want it,

668
00:34:43,610 --> 00:34:46,070
the position of Ning State's
Prime Minister

669
00:34:46,739 --> 00:34:48,260
will always be kept for Yue Chi.
